text: Elias Salhab (born 18 March 1925) is a Lebanese former sports shooter. He competed at the 1960, 1968 and the 1972 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1925 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Lebanese male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Lebanon Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1968 Summer Olympics Category:Shooters at the 1972 Summer Olympics
